## Easily build applications for any scenario using a comprehensive and integrated data portfolio

Microsoft offers a variety of database products and services that are built to address your specific business needs. In addition, we make it easy and cost-effective to migrate your existing databases to Azure by using the [Azure Database Migration Service](https://azure.microsoft.com/services/database-migration/).

### Microsoft database services

