| **IF YOU'RE LOOKING FOR...** | **THEN USE…** | **PRODUCT TYPE** |
|:--- |:--- |:--- |
| A fully managed relational database that provisions quickly, scales on the fly, and includes built-in intelligence and security… | [Azure SQL Database](https://azure.microsoft.com/services/sql-database/ "Opens the Azure SQL Database marketing page") | Relational database |
| A fully managed service that provides out-of-the-box support for most SQL Server features and accompanying tools and services as well as native virtual network (VNET) support for an isolated, highly-secure environment to run your applications… | [Azure SQL Database Managed Instance](https://azuremarketplace.microsoft.com/marketplace/apps/Microsoft.SQLManagedInstance "Opens the Azure SQL Database Managed Instance marketplace page") | Relational database |
| A fully managed service that makes it easy to reduce your capital investments and optimize operational expenses by migrating your on-premises SQL Server to the cloud… | [SQL Server on Virtual Machines](https://azure.microsoft.com/services/virtual-machines/sql-server/ "Opens the SQL Server on Azure VMs marketing page") | Relational database |
| A fully managed service that allows independent scaling of compute and storage, while pausing and resuming your data warehouse within minutes through a massively parallel processing architecture... | [Azure SQL Data Warehouse](https://azure.microsoft.com/services/sql-data-warehouse/?v=17.44 "Opens the Azure SQL Data Warehouse marketing page") | Data warehouse |
